# Snake Game

## About

A classic Snake game made using Python Turtle.
Built to sharpen my logic and understand how simple games work from scratch — no fancy libraries, just clean code and fun movement.

## Features

* Smooth snake movement
* Growing tail after eating food
* Score tracking
* Game over detection
* Simple and minimal look

## Controls

* Move Up → `Up Arrow`
* Move Down → `Down Arrow`
* Move Left → `Left Arrow`
* Move Right → `Right Arrow`

## How to Play

1. Clone the repo

   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/Sharan-Kumar-707/The-Snake-Game.git
   ```
2. Open the folder

   ```bash
   cd snake-game
   ```
3. Run the game

   ```bash
   python main.py
   ```
4. Eat the food, grow longer, and avoid hitting yourself!

## Built With

* Python
* Turtle Graphics

